data.description: Discover your dream home in Kendall, Florida! Nestled in a prime location, this spacious residence is surrounded by excellent schools and major highways, ensuring convenience and connectivity. Boasting a new garage door, A/C system, and appliances, this large house is the epitome of modern comfort. The open floor plan seamlessly connects living spaces, perfect for entertaining. Imagine the joy of returning to a meticulously landscaped backyard after a busy day. Don't miss this opportunity to embrace the perfect blend of luxury and tranquility in a beautiful Kendall neighborhood. Schedule a showing and make this house your home today!
